Question: Who is the young person to the left of the chair sitting beside?

Reference Answer: gentleman

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n281241.jpg

Original program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='chair')
IMAGE0=CROP_LEFTOF(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='young person')
IMAGE1=CROP_BEHIND(image=IMAGE0,box=BOX1)
BOX2=LOC(image=IMAGE1,object='young person')
ANSWER0=COUNT(box=BOX2)
ANSWER1=EVAL(expr="'young person' if {ANSWER0} > 0 else 'no one'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER1)
```
